    "title": "LESSON 57: THE '-AD-' SUFFIX",
    "header_color": "green",
    "pages": [
      {
        "page": 1,
        "total_pages": 1,
        "content": [
          "The suffix -AD- means \"continuous action\" or",
          "\"repeated action.\" It emphasizes duration or",
          "ongoing process rather than a single act.",
          "",
          "FROM VERB TO CONTINUOUS ACTION:",
          "paroli  → parolado    = speak → speaking",
          "kanti   → kantado     = sing → singing",
          "labori  → laborado    = work → working",
          "lerni   → lernado     = learn → learning",
          "",
          "THE DIFFERENCE:",
          "parolo   = a speech (single thing)",
          "parolado = speaking (the act, ongoing)",
          "",
          "IN USE:",
          "La lernado daŭris du horojn.",
          "(The studying lasted two hours.)",
          "-AD- turns moments into processes!"
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Leciono kvindek sep"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "lesson_id": "058",
    "trigger_word": "kun estimo",
    "title": "LESSON 58: THE '-IST-' SUFFIX",
    "header_color": "green",
    "pages": [
      {
        "page": 1,
        "total_pages": 1,
        "content": [
          "The suffix -IST- creates words for people",
          "who do something professionally or",
          "habitually. Think \"specialist.\"",
          "",
          "CONSTRUCTING TITLES:",
          "arto    → artisto     = art → artist",
          "muziko  → muzikisto   = music → musician",
          "instrui → instruisto  = teach → teacher",
          "dento   → dentisto    = tooth → dentist",
          "Esperanto → Esperantisto = Esperantist",
          "",
          "COMPARE -ANT- AND -IST-:",
          "lernanto = learner (anyone learning now)",
          "lernisto = scholar (professional learner)",
          "instruanto = one teaching (right now)",
          "instruisto = teacher (profession)",
          "",
          "-IST- implies expertise or dedication!"
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Leciono kvindek ok"
      }
    ]
  },
